iOnRoad,is,an,application,for,mobile,phones,to,help,drivers,navigate,their,way,through,driving,iOnRoad,provides,traffic,information,collision,warnings,and,features,to,make,calling,and,talking,easier,while,driving,The,iOnRoad,API,allows,developers,to,access,and,integrate,the,functionality,of,iOnRoad,with,other,applications,Public,API,access,is,not,available,interested,developers,should,email,team,ionroad,com,for,more,information